        "subject": "LU-3189 tests: add version check code into sanity test 53",
        "message": "LU-3189 tests: add version check code into sanity test 53\n\nThis patch adds Lustre version check codes into sanity test\n53 to make the test work with servers that have the following\npatches:\n\nLustre-commit: d17fd58c07d102ffee8dfb64f300ef26532ffc98\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/6106\nand\nLustre-commit: 6c4c51e3079e6c257fbf86536e4739110c166e3b\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/4789\n\nTest-Parameters: envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ENABLE_QUOTA=yes,ONLY=53 \\\nclientdistro=el6 ossdistro=el6 mdsdistro=el6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nossarch=x86_64 mdsarch=x86_64 \\\nossjob=lustre-b2_4 mdsjob=lustre-b2_4 ossbuildno=70 mdsbuildno=70 \\\ntestlist=sanity\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie36cf7c9faa664b7e95b5e25e9696a355adf0870\n"
